v0.2 (2011/02/25):
- Revamped dictionary editing, created a new interface through which you
can now delete from the dictionary
- Fixed bugs: crash when opening several dictionaries, pressing
enter on the last form line caused quizzes to advance

v0.1 (2011/02/20):
- Can create or open an existing dictionary
- Can add/edit words to/from the dictionary. No possibility of deleting
  words yet.
- Simple 3 nouns/3 verbs/3 adjectives quiz
- Detailed 3 nouns/3 verbs/3 adjectives quiz

